end note

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
'  CORE — VolumeRenderCoordinator (thin MonoBehaviour shell)
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
class VolumeRenderCoordinator {
  ' ── Injected collaborators ─────────────────────────
  - _materialBinder  : VolumeMaterialBinder
  - _textureManager  : VolumeTextureManager
  - _cameraDriver    : VolumeCameraDriver
  - _foveatedPolicy  : FoveatedSamplingPolicy

  ' ── Unity lifecycle (pure delegation — no domain logic) ─
  + Start()       : void   ' delegates to _textureManager.Load()
  + Update()      : void   ' delegates SyncShaderState + BindFrame
  + OnDestroy()   : void   ' delegates Dispose()
}

note bottom of VolumeRenderCoordinator
  <b>Projected CK Metrics</b>
  ─────────────────────────────
  WMC  ~ 3   (≤ 20 target ✅)
  CBO  ~ 6   (≤ 25 orchestrator ✅)
  RFC  ~ 12  (≤ 50 target ✅)
  LCOM ~ 0.0 (≤ 0.5 target ✅)
  LOC  ~ 40
  ─────────────────────────────
  T-02 trade-off: must extend
  MonoBehaviour — unavoidable Unity
  dependency. Mitigated: < 30 lines,
  zero domain logic.
end note

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
'  CORE — VolumeMaterialBinder
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
class VolumeMaterialBinder {
  ' ── Dependencies (interface only — DIP) ────────────
  - _renderPipeline  : IRenderPipeline
  - _activeMaskMode  : IMaskMode

  ' ── Material instances ─────────────────────────────
  - _materialInstance     : Material
  - _maskMaterialInstance : Material
  - _ids                  : MaterialID   ' cached Shader.PropertyToID

  ' ── Scaling / threshold state ──────────────────────
  - _scalingType     : ScalingType
  - _scalingBias     : float
  - _scalingContrast : float
  - _scalingAlpha    : float
  - _thresholdMin    : float
  - _thresholdMax    : float
  - _colorMap        : ColorMapEnum

  ' ── Public API ─────────────────────────────────────
  + SyncShaderState() : void         ' replaces 25+ SetFloat calls in Update()
  + SetMaskMode(mode : IMaskMode)    ' strategy swap — zero switch statements
  + SetColourMap(map : ColorMapEnum)
  + ShiftColourMap(delta : int)
  + ResetThresholds()
  + Dispose()
}

note bottom of VolumeMaterialBinder
  <b>Projected CK Metrics</b>
  ─────────────────────────────
  WMC  ~ 8   (≤ 20 target ✅)
  CBO  ~ 5   (≤ 14 domain ✅)
  RFC  ~ 18  (≤ 50 target ✅)
  LCOM ~ 0.0 (≤ 0.5 target ✅)
  LOC  ~ 150
  ─────────────────────────────
  All SRP keyword calls proxied
  through IRenderPipeline only.
  No direct URP/HDRP imports.
end note

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
'  CORE — VolumeTextureManager
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
class VolumeTextureManager {
  ' ── Data source (interface only) ───────────────────
  - _dataSource      : IRawVolumeData
  - _maskDataSource  : IRawVolumeData

  ' ── Budget enforcement ─────────────────────────────
  - _budgetBytes     : long           ' default: 368 MB
  - _maxTextureCap   : long           ' hard cap: 4 GB (Unity limit)

  ' ── Texture state ──────────────────────────────────
  - _dataCube   : Texture3D
  - _maskCube   : Texture3D
  - _filterMode : FilterMode          ' always Point (scientific invariant)

  ' ── Public API ─────────────────────────────────────
  + EnsureTextureReady() : Texture3D
  + GenerateDownsampledCube()
  + RegenerateCubes()
  + Evict()
  + Dispose()
}

note bottom of VolumeTextureManager
  <b>Projected CK Metrics</b>
  ─────────────────────────────
  WMC  ~ 6   (≤ 20 target ✅)
  CBO  ~ 4   (≤ 14 domain ✅)
  RFC  ~ 14  (≤ 50 target ✅)
  LCOM ~ 0.0 (≤ 0.5 target ✅)
  LOC  ~ 130
  ─────────────────────────────
  Single enforcement point for:
  • 4 GB Texture3D ceiling
  • 368 MB default budget
  • FilterMode.Point invariant
end note

